Saelben's Space Program

The Backstory

Spoiler

As the dust settles, the last of the Kerbals awaken, confusedly roaming their bases, wondering what happened. One of them is Jeb, waking up, rubbing the dust out of his eyes, and wondering what happened.

Although they don't know it yet, a terrible generic plotmoving disaster has happened.

Where is everyone? What happened? Asks Jeb,in an attempt to keep the tiny bit of nonexistant plot even vaguely intriguing.

Except for them few, there doesn't seem to be a living soul anywhere, and noone is answering the comms signals.

Jeb looks around himself at all the hungry, sad and desparate faces of his fellow Kerbonauts, and decides something must be done, they must find out what happened...
